Value: LBT Innovations Limited engages in the research, development, and commercialization of technologies for the healthcare and laboratory supply markets in Australia and Switzerland. The company offers MicroStreak, an automated culture-plate streaking and inoculation system; and Automated Plate Assessment System, a platform technology that automates culture-plate screening and interpretation. It also develops Automated Gram Strain Assessment for the automated interpretation of gram stain image analysis; WoundVue, a technology that uses artificial intelligence to assist clinicians in the assessment and care of chronic wounds; and devices that can detect biofilms in the presence of mammalian tissue. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Adelaide, Australia.
